<HEADLINE> 5 Die After Drinking Contaminated Water in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, August 10 (Xinhua) -- Five people died and 20 others
were hospitalized after drinking contaminated water in India's
Punjab State on Saturday night, the Press Trust of India reported
today.
