<HEADLINE> International Symposium on Hepatology Held </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 11 (Xinhua) -- An International Symposium on
Hepatology, one of the world's highest-level academic conferences
in its field, opened here today.
</P>
<P>
More than 800 hepatologists and doctors will attend the
five-day symposium, sponsored by the China Association for Science
and Technology (CAS), to discuss advances in the diagnosis,
treatment, and prevention of different types of hepatitis and
liver-related diseases and the latest developments in hepatology.
</P>
<P>
Twenty-three of the world's most famous hepatologists and 17
Chinese scholars will speak on various topics. There will also be
three seminars on the treatment of viral hepatitis and liver
transplants.
</P>
