16 cents to finish at 0.56 Singapore dollar. The United Overseas
Bank (UOB) Foreign gained ten cents to end at 13.8 Singapore
dollars, while the Singapore Technologies Aero closed nine cents
higher at 2.02 Singapore dollars.
</P>
