declined 4.3 dollars to end at 8.9 Singapore dollars. Creative 50
fell 2.8 dollars to close at 30.8 Singapore dollars. Malaya
Banking 200 lost 2.5 dollars to finish at 12 Singapore dollars,
while the Asean Fund was one dollar lower at 15.4 U.S. dollars.
