in Lebanon for the first time.
</P>
<P>
The camp was organized by the Ministry of Emigrant Affairs and
the Ministry of Education.
</P>
<P>
"This is the first time in the history of Lebanon that
something like this has been organised, and we are hoping to make
this a yearly activity for all age groups," he added.
</P>
<P>
According to official statistics, there are more than 10
million Lebanese expatriates all over the world.
</P>
<P>
