potable water supply system which will be installed this month in
the central province of Visayas.
</P>
<P>
Garilao said the installation of the water supply systems will
benefit more than 903 households comprising at least 6,517
farmer-beneficiaries of the comprehensive agrarian reform program
and residents.
</P>
<P>
He added that about 21 projects involving farm-to-market roads,
potable water systems, multi-purpose pavements, multi-purpose
halls, and irrigation projects will be realized next month.
