<HEADLINE> Mantilla Wins San Marino Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, August 10 (Xinhua) -- Felix Mantilla of Spain defeated
Magnus Gustafsson of Sweden in straight sets to take the San
Marino International tournament title on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Top-seeded Mantilla, ranked 12th in the world, captured his
fourth tournament title of the year by downing Gustafsson 6-4, 6-1
for a prize money of 39,000 US dollars. 
</P>
